data.description: Experience lakefront living at its finest in this charming 2 bed, 2 bath retreat nestled on the shores of beautiful Lake Lanier. Boasting a newly renovated party dock, complete with electric, floats, and ample space for entertaining, this property is a water lover's dream. Step inside to discover a freshly updated interior, featuring a new roof, paint, and appliances, ensuring both style and functionality. Outside, lush landscaping frames stunning lake views, inviting you to relax and unwind in serene surroundings. Whether you're seeking a weekend getaway or a year-round oasis, this lake house offers the perfect blend of comfort and recreation. Don't miss your chance to own a slice of lakeside paradise!
